---
// About Me Component
---

<section id="about" class="container">
  <h2 class="section-title fade-in">About Me</h2>

  <!-- 60:40 Split Profile Dashboard -->
  <div class="about-hero-grid fade-in">
    <div class="about-narrative">
      <span class="about-greeting">Who I Am</span>
      <h3 class="about-name">Chaiyapong Jaroonrotjananan</h3>
      
      <div class="about-titles">
        <span class="title-tag">Software Engineer</span>
        <span class="title-tag">Full-stack Developer</span>
        <span class="title-tag">Back-end Developer</span>
      </div>

      <p class="about-bio">
        I am a Computer Engineering graduate from Kasetsart University (Kamphaeng Saen Campus) with a strong passion for Software Engineering and Full-stack Development. I specialize in building highly structured backend systems while delivering clean, responsive user interfaces. 
      </p>
      <p class="about-bio">
        During my cooperative education internship as a <strong>Full-stack Developer</strong> at <strong>App InTouch Co Ltd</strong>, I gained hands-on experience by upgrading enterprise budget systems. I excel at handling evolving client requirements, optimizing slow queries, and improving page initial loading times using modern performance techniques.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Quick Stats Card -->
    <div class="about-stats-card">
      <div class="card-glow-overlay"></div>
      <h4 class="card-title">Professional Snapshot</h4>
      
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-icon-wrapper">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="stat-icon"><path d="M22 10v6M2 10l10-5 10 5-10 5z"></path><path d="M6 12v5c0 2 2 3 6 3s6-1 6-3v-5"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-details">
          <span class="stat-label">Education</span>
          <span class="stat-value">B.Eng. Computer Engineering <br/><small class="text-dim">Kasetsart University (KPS)</small></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-icon-wrapper">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="stat-icon"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-details">
          <span class="stat-label">Cooperative Internship</span>
          <span class="stat-value">Full-stack Developer <br/><small class="text-dim">App InTouch Co Ltd</small></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-icon-wrapper">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="stat-icon"><polygon points="12 2 2 7 12 12 22 7 12 2</polygon><polyline points="2 17 12 22 22 17"></polyline><polyline points="2 12 12 17 22 12"></polyline></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-details">
          <span class="stat-label">Key Core Focus</span>
          <span class="stat-value">Backend Systems & UI Optimization</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-icon-wrapper">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="stat-icon"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"></line><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"></line></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-details">
          <span class="stat-label">Dev Philosophy</span>
          <span class="stat-value font-italic">"Optimize early, code cleanly, scale efficiently."</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Three-Pillar Core Achievements Grid -->
  <h3 class="subsection-title fade-in">Co-op Internship Accomplishments</h3>
  <div class="about-pillars-grid fade-in">
    <!-- Pillar 1 -->
    <div class="pillar-card">
      <div class="pillar-icon-box">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"></polygon></svg>
      </div>
      <h4 class="pillar-title">Performance Optimization</h4>
      <p class="pillar-desc">
        Designed and developed a data retrieval module featuring <strong>Tab-based Lazy Loading</strong> to solve system lag, drastically reducing initial page load times and creating a highly fluid UI experience for enterprise users.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Pillar 2 -->
    <div class="pillar-card">
      <div class="pillar-icon-box">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"></path><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"></polyline><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"></line><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"></line><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"></polyline></svg>
      </div>
      <h4 class="pillar-title">Logic & Reporting Engine</h4>
      <p class="pillar-desc">
        Upgraded the legacy budget reporting module, refactoring <strong>7-8 reports</strong> and designing <strong>2 new highly complex reports</strong>, while implementing an automated <strong>Excel export</strong> engine with custom styling for instant analysis.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Pillar 3 -->
    <div class="pillar-card">
      <div class="pillar-icon-box">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"></ellipse><path d="M3 5V19A9 3 0 0 0 21 19V5"></path><path d="M3 12A9 3 0 0 0 21 12"></path></svg>
      </div>
      <h4 class="pillar-title">APIs & Relational Databases</h4>
      <p class="pillar-desc">
        Developed complex business logic and large-scale budget calculations using <strong>ASP.NET Core (C#)</strong> and Razor, collaborating with internal APIs and optimizing database connectivity for maximum performance and accuracy.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Structured Skill Matrix -->
  <h3 class="subsection-title fade-in">Technical Skill Matrix</h3>
  <div class="about-skills-matrix fade-in">
    <!-- Production Stacks -->
    <div class="skills-card core-skills">
      <div class="skills-header">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="skills-group-icon"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"></path></svg>
        <h4>Production-Tested Stack</h4>
      </div>
      <p class="skills-sub">Actively utilized in a professional team setting during my cooperative education internship.</p>
      
      <div class="skill-category">
        <span class="category-name">Backend Framework</span>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="tag tag-glow">.NET Core</span>
          <span class="tag tag-glow">C#</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="skill-category">
        <span class="category-name">Database Systems</span>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="tag tag-glow">Oracle SQL</span>
          <span class="tag tag-glow">Relational Databases</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="skill-category">
        <span class="category-name">System & Tools</span>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="tag tag-glow">Azure DevOps (Version Control)</span>
          <span class="tag tag-glow">Razor Pages</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Exploratory Playground & Other Skills -->
    <div class="skills-card playground-skills">
      <div class="skills-header">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="skills-group-icon"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="M8 12h8"></path><path d="M12 8v8"></path></svg>
        <h4>Playground & Other Skills</h4>
      </div>
      <p class="skills-sub">Other technologies, frameworks, and tools explored through personal projects and self-study.</p>
      
      <div class="skill-category">
        <span class="category-name">Backend Frameworks</span>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="tag">Spring Boot (Java)</span>
          <span class="tag">FastAPI (Python)</span>
          <span class="tag">Laravel (PHP)</span>
          <span class="tag">Express.js (Node.js)</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-category">
        <span class="category-name">Frontend Ecosystem</span>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="tag">React</span>
          <span class="tag">Next.js</span>
          <span class="tag">Astro</span>
          <span class="tag">Tailwind CSS</span>
          <span class="tag">Bootstrap</span>
          <span class="tag">Ant Design</span>
          <span class="tag">Material UI</span>
          <span class="tag">HTML5 / CSS3 / JS</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="skill-category">
        <span class="category-name">Databases & Tools</span>
        <div class="skill-tags">
          <span class="tag">PostgreSQL</span>
          <span class="tag">MySQL</span>
          <span class="tag">SQL Server</span>
          <span class="tag">Git / GitHub</span>
          <span class="tag">Swagger API</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #about.container {
    padding-bottom: 80px;
  }

  .subsection-title {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  /* === 60:40 Split Layout === */
  .about-hero-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .about-narrative {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .about-greeting {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .about-name {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .about-titles {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  .title-tag {
    background-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.08);
    color: var(--accent);
    padding: 0.35rem 0.85rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.12);
  }

  .about-bio {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .about-bio strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  /* === Profile Snapshot Card === */
  .about-stats-card {
    background-color: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .about-stats-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.05);
  }

  .card-glow-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    right: -50%;
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.08) 0%, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0) 70%);
    border-radius: 50%;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .card-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .stat-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .stat-icon-wrapper {
    width: 2.5rem;
    height: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    background-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.08);
    color: var(--accent);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
  }

  .stat-icon {
    stroke-width: 2px;
  }

  .stat-details {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.15rem;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .stat-value {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .text-dim {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .font-italic {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  /* === Three-Pillar Achievements === */
  .about-pillars-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .pillar-card {
    background-color: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2.2rem;
    transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  }

  .pillar-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
  }

  .pillar-icon-box {
    width: 3rem;
    height: 3rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.08);
    color: var(--accent);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.12);
  }

  .pillar-title {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .pillar-desc {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .pillar-desc strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  /* === Skill Matrix === */
  .about-skills-matrix {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }

  .skills-card {
    background-color: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    position: relative;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .skills-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  /* Glimmer border effect for core production skills */
  .core-skills {
    border-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.25);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.02);
  }

  .core-skills:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.06);
  }

  .skills-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .skills-group-icon {
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .skills-header h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .skills-sub {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .skill-category {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .skill-category:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .category-name {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .skill-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.6rem;
  }

  .tag {
    background-color: var(--bg-primary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.25s ease;
  }

  .tag:hover {
    background-color: var(--accent);
    border-color: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  /* Glimmer style tag for production stack */
  .tag-glow {
    background-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.05);
    border-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.25);
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .tag-glow:hover {
    background-color: var(--accent);
    border-color: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15);
  }

  /* === Responsive Layout Adjustments === */
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .about-pillars-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }

    .about-skills-matrix {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .about-hero-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr;
    }
  }
</style>
